pullrequest.title: SVG support for arcs, disjoints paths and their triangulation / extrusion

content.raw:
I found that capsule.svg is located in `test/data/` and not `test/data/svg/` so I think that's why the test is producing this msg:

~~~
[Err] [SVGLoader.cc:663] Failed to load file /home/ian/depot/clones/gazebo6/test/data/svg/capsule.svg
~~~

However this test passes, does that mean `Parse` always returns true?
